Go to
HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Policies\Microsoft\Windows\Windows Search
and change DWORD strings
AllowCloudSearch
AllowCortana
AllowSearchToUseLocation
ConnectedSearchUseWeb
ConnectedSearchUseWebOverMeteredConnections
to
0

and change DWORD strings
ConnectedSearchPrivacy
ConnectedSearchSafeSearch
to
3

and change DWORD string
DisableWebSearch
to
1

&

Go to
HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Policies\Microsoft\SearchCompanion
and change DWORD string
DisableContentFileUpdates
to
1


Finish.
